    - init_persistence_from_env: wraps live client in translator + sets
      MDB_MCP_READ_ONLY=false (read-only default hid all write tools).
    - mcp.py: lazy google.cloud.secretmanager import (MCPClient usable without
      GCP SDK on dev boxes).
    - Evidence: 6/6 CRUD round-trip vs REAL mongod 7.0.14 + REAL npm MCP server
      through the production stdio client. 38 new tests; 585-test suite green
      (1 pre-existing data_fetch docstring failure, untouched).
    
